TEXT.Text:
{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Defeat 12 Ash Wolves

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - Oliver

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dispatch 12 Ash Wolves at South Windia Plains and report to Oliver in Odelia!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver the Recommendation to Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Guard Captain Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Now's our chance to join the Dragon Fellowship! Go to Colin and give him Dustin's recommendation!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Defeat 15 Starry Lolos

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Guard Captain Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
The alarming increase in monsters around Port of the Winds is making life hard for all the people. Slay {C=0xFF016295/}15 Starry Lolo{C=0xFF4D0D08/} around the Port and report to Captain Colin.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Defeat 7 Woodies

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - Equipment Merchant Billy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
In the name of justice you should slay the {C=0xFF016295/}7 Woodies{C=0xFF4D0D08/} that destroyed the farmer's land. Don't forget to tell Billy afterwards.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Find Children's Shoes, Bag and Lunchbox

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Guard Captain Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Report to Guard Captain Colin after finding the traces of the children at Skippy Sanctuary, where they were taken.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Give notice to Lord Steven Jr. in Port of the Winds and report to Guard Captain Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Guard Captain Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Report to Evan after obtaining permission from the Lord to put notices on the village board in order to find the children who were abducted by the monsters.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver a letter to Pet Merchant Edith

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Libra - Pet Merchant Edith

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver Amy's letter to Edith, Amy's sister. She is located at the merchant village of Libra.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver a report to Captain Dustin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - Guard Captain Dustin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Retrieve the report of chaos that erupted 50 years ago and deliver it to {C=0xFF016295/}Guard Captain Dustin in Odelia{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver General Blood's Journal to Alvin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Report to Dustin after you deliver the Journal

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Return to Dustin after handing the diary and memo of General Blood to Alvin for deciphering.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver Ink Sample to General Merchant Heidi

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - General Merchant Heidi

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver the {C=0xFF016295/}Ink Sample{C=0xFF4D0D08/} to Heidi so she can inspect General Blood's Journal.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver Ink Sample to Trade Merchant Heidi.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - General Merchant Heidi

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Blacksmith Darwin discovered the cryptic memo. Deliver this memo to {C=0xFF016295/}Dustin{C=0xFF4D0D08/}!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Get 20 Spider Poisons

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - General Merchant Heidi

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Collect {C=0xFF016295/}20 Spider Poisons{C=0xFF4D0D08/} for Heidi so she could create the Ink Neutralizer.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver the Ink Neutralizer to Alvin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - Reclusive Old Man Alvin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
I've finally finished producing the chemical that dissolves the ink. Now, deliver this to Alvin!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Look for Daisy and deliver the production order

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Advanced Windia Plains - General Merchant Daisy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver the {C=0xFF016295/}Production Order{C=0xFF4D0D08/} to Daisy in Advanced Windia Plains.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Get 15 Raccoon Hides and 15 Long Tails

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Advanced Windia Plains - General Merchant Daisy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
We need materials to replicate the page. The materials are {C=0xFF016295/}15 Raccoon Hide and 15 Long Tail{C=0xFF4D0D08/}, found at Traitor's Ridge. Give them to Daisy after collecting them.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver Diary Page to Alvin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - Reclusive Old Man Alvin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver the copied page to Alvin in Odelia.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver the report to Lord Steven Jr. at Port of the Winds

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Lord Steven Jr.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver a copy of the {C=0xFF016295/}Report of General Blood's Journal{C=0xFF4D0D08/} to {C=0xFF016295/}Lord Steven Jr. at Port of the Winds{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Hunt Ash Wolves, Woodies and Spees

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - Guard Captain Dustin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Slay {C=0xFF016295/}5 Ash Wolves, 5 Woodies and 5 Spees{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. Report to Dustin afterwards.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Acquire Vagabond's Heart

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - Guard Captain Dustin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Bring the most important item for the 'Legendary Warriors' festival. The {C=0xFF016295/}Vagabond's Heart from Windia Plains' Mission Map (1 Star or more){C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Defeat {C=0xFF016295/}Lord of Night{C=0xFF4D0D08/}, the captain of monsters!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Guard Captain Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Enter the {C=0xFF016295/}Mirinae Sanctuary Mission Map (1 Star or more){C=0xFF4D0D08/} and slay {C=0xFF016295/}Lord of Night{C=0xFF4D0D08/}!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Ask expert's opinion for Mysterious Gloves from Anders.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Runaway Miner Turner

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Visit Blacksmith Anders in Libra and let him appraise the Mysterious Gloves. Return to Turner after.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Receive Mysterious Gloves from Anders

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Runaway Miner Turner

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Visit Blacksmith Davy in Libra and let him appraise the mysterious gloves. Return to Turner after.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver General Blood's Gauntlets to Guard Captain Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Blacksmith Anders

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Go to Guard Captain Colin at Port of the Winds. He will investigate General Blood's Gauntlets.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver General Blood's Gauntlets to Guard Captain Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Guard Captain Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Go to Guard Captain Colin at Port of the Winds. He will investigate General Blood's Gauntlets.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver Horn Ornament to James at Port of the Winds

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Real Estate Agent James

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
There is a rumour that {C=0xFF016295/}Guard Balder in Libra{C=0xFF4D0D08/} found what is supposedly a Dragon Horn Ornament from the ruins. Scholars believe that it would be of great help for their study so they insist on acquiring this {C=0xFF016295/}Horn Ornament{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Speak to Blacksmith Darwin in Odelia

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - Blacksmith Darwin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Darwin discovered a suspicious piece of paper. Go get that paper from Darwin as Dustin requested.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Gather 20 Sapphire Spadestones

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Blacksmith Anders

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Anders in Libra will exchange 1 Jade Cloverstone and 5 gold for every 20 Sapphire Spadestones.

Welcome to {C=0xFFFFFF11/}Odelia!{C=0xFFFFFFFF/}
Currently you're in the {C=0xFFFFFF11/}Backalley{C=0xFFFFFFFF/}.
Talk to me if you wish to know more about the game functions!

