Currently you're in the {C=0xFFFFFF11/}Backalley{C=0xFFFFFFFF/}.
Talk to me if you wish to know more about the game functions!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Defeat 15 Shark Deckhands and Shark Pirates

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Guard Captain Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
According to the information from the scouts, pirates have settled along the coasts of the Port of the Winds. Defeat all of them and report to Colin!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Talk to Innkeeper Florence

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Innkeeper Florence

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
We've finally arrived in Odelia!
Oliver has directed us to the Inn and advised us to socialize with the local folks. Use the {C=0xFF016295/}N key and mouse cursor to find Florence{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Tutorial - Basic Steps

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Adelio, the Bounty Hunter

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Let's learn the basics of combat from Adelio.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver the ancient magic scroll

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - Senior Magician Edeline

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
The Warrior Academy is going to wage war with the monsters at Port of the Winds. Pablo has heard of this, and wishes to provide Edeline with the magic scroll.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver a copy of the Magic Scroll to Sage Jeremy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Sage Jeremy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Edeline has some problems translating the scroll. She's recorded the contents and asked you to deliver it to Jeremy.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Collect 5 Sticky Fluids and 20 Shadow Papers

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Sage Jeremy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Sage Jeremy accidentally damaged the ancient magic book.
He's requested us to find the materials to repair it.
Find 5 Sticky Fluid and 20 Shadow Papers. They can be obtained from Lava Boombooms and Mace Mummies at Valid Raeth.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Meet the Fungoid Chief in the Mushroom Village

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Mushroom Village - Fungoid Chief

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Sage Jeremy needs an ancient lexicon to translate the text.
The Fungoid Chief is the only person who has one.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
30 Fairydust and 30 Plant Poison

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Completion NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - InnKeeper Mosanra

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
The Fungoid Village's final request:
Lately, the Fungoid villagers have fallen ill.%%
Gather 30 Fairydust and Plant Poison from the Land of Temptation.
Turn them in to Inkeeper Mosanra.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Bring back Healing Treestump

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Completion NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - Chief Massirun

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Chief Massirun doesn't like humans yet.
Bringing the Healing Treestump from the Karkarous in Gods' Sanctuary have stolen, and it will change his mind!
Get the Healing Treestump and return to Chief Massirun!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Defeat Mimir King, BuboBubo

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Fungoid Village - Chief Fungarf

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Mimir King, BuboBubo is trying to invade the now-weakened Fungoid Village.
Slay BuboBubo for Chief Fungarf to recover the relationship between humans and Fungoidkind!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Meet Warrior Commander Evan

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Warrior Commander Evan

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Being part of the Dragon Fellowship ain't easy. The recruitment for the second team will begin shortly. Until then, we need to train hard!
Speak to Warrior Commander Evan and train with him, just as Colin instructed!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Gather 10 Ruby Heartstones

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - General Merchant Heidi

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Shinestones can be traded for other items at Port of the Winds.
Be sure to try it out when you're seasoned enough to combat the monsters there!
Give {C=0xFF016295/}10 Ruby Heartstones to Heidi as thanks for her information{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Give Papyrus to Guard Guppy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - Guard Guppy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
{C=0xFF016295/}Get Papyrus by helping people then give it to Guppy{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Get 10 Plain Wood

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - Wine Merchant Pamela

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Pamela said she needs {C=0xFF016295/}Plain Wood{C=0xFF4D0D08/} to make matches. Get 10 Plain Wood for her. You can get them from {C=0xFF016295/}Woodi's{C=0xFF4D0D08/} at Windia Plains.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Let Heidi know that Alvin needs a special liquid to remove the ink

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - General Merchant Heidi

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Alvin needs a special chemical to remove the ink, so that he can continue deciphering General Blood's Journal. Explain to {C=0xFF016295/}Heidi{C=0xFF4D0D08/} what Alvin needs.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver the old fashioned Papyrus to Alvin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Odelia - Reclusive Old Man Alvin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver the old fashioned Papyrus to {C=0xFF016295/}Alvin{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver Alvin's recommendation letter to Guard Captain Colin

