{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Wind/Libra - Randy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Werewolf and Dracula who were harassing Randy turned out to be real monsters! If so, could the Pumpkin Cafe Waiter who saved Randy be a real monster also?
Let's defeat the Pumpkin Cafe Waiter in All Mission Maps (Lv.3 and Lv.4) of the continent to get 3 Pumpkin Cookies and 3 Pumpkin Jellies from him.

When you finish the Mission Mode, you will see the Rank, you can see the Rank in real time in the bottom right of your screen. There is a criterion for the Rank.
{C=0xFF016295/}[Sense]{C=0xFFFFFFFF/}
Sense gauge will fill up with normal attacks..
When the character is hit from a monster or cannot be moved, the gauge will decrease.
{C=0xFF016295/}[Ability]{C=0xFFFFFFFF/}
Ability gauge will fill up with skill attack.

