Odelia - Dun Morgan

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
After heroes left Odelia, monsters appeared and the tourists returned who actually wanted to go Port of the Winds. Dun Morgan wants to know some more information from {C=0xFF016295/}merchants in the village{C=0xFF4D0D08/} so {C=0xFF016295/}I have to collect{C=0xFF4D0D08/}the information.

{C=0xFF00863C/}(roused to anger){C=0xFF4D0D08/}
You see, this nose is red because of what the freezing weather did to me!%%
Old lady, your nose is red too!

{C=0xFF00863C/}(Suddenly he stood up and shouted.){C=0xFF4D0D08/}
You useless red nose!%%
{C=0xFF00863C/}(Clenching his fist){C=0xFF4D0D08/}
You want me to make that nose red like the sun?!?
